nodes.text: Qalsneek the Bull was a male Swimmer from Dellalt. He was a Jedi Master during the Great Sith War. He was responsible for many of the water-culture artifacts evacuated from Ossus, following its destruction in the Cron Drift supernova. He hid them beneath the seas of Kamino, in the Derem City ruins, along with his own holocron.
